  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Adds definitions of \"identifier\" and \"specified data element\" and amends the definition of \"personal information\" for the purposes of notifying affected persons of data and security breaches under the State's data breach notification law.  Includes telecommunications carriers subject to and in compliance with certain federal provisions among the businesses deemed compliant with this law.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
    }
  ],
